Black doesn't have} 6... e5 {, as} 7. Nf5 Bxf5 8. exf5 d5 9. Bg5 d4 10. Ne4 Be7
11. Bxf6 gxf6 12. Be2 Qa5+ 13. Kf1 Nc6 14. a3 Rc8 15. Rb1 Qc7 16. Qg3 Rf8 17.
Bd3 $16 {is just excellent.}) (6... Nbd7 {Approved as the theoretically best
move.} 7. Be2 $1 e6 (7... g6 8. Bg5 Bg7 9. O-O-O O-O 10. f4 (10. Qd2) 10... Qc7
11. h4 e5 12. Nb3 h6 13. f5 $40) (7... Nc5 8. Qe3 e5 9. Nb3 $14) 8. O-O b5 9.
b4 $1 {All of a sudden, White starts a queenside attack.} Bb7 10. a4 bxa4 11.
